CBRE and DWP Property are pleased to present 46 Edward Street, Summer Hill to the market for lease.

Fully Approved for 9B Educational Use with Inner West Council, the premises is a multi-level office building with up to 2,270sqm* of space to occupy.

Key Features:

•	New air-conditioning throughout
•	New lift being installed for accessibility and DDA compliance
•	Existing fit out includes kitchenettes, boardrooms, existing classrooms and recently refurbished amenities
•	Building naming rights (STCA)
•	Ability to integrate tenants fit out if alterations required
•	9B approval: suitable for colleges, schools, tutoring companies, educational institutions and RTO’s
•	9 car spaces

There is added convenience and ease of access for staff/students as 46 Edward St is only metres away from Lewisham Light Rail and 2 minutes’ walk from Summer Hill and Lewisham Train Stations, shops, popular cafes and other community amenities.

Contact the listed Exclusively Appointed agents to attain more information and to arrange a private inspection at your convenience.
